_json.gridTitle: The Best Chicken You Will Ever Eat. Ever.
_json.description: Moroccan Dipping Sauce:     1/4 cup lemon juice     1 medium clove garlic, crushed     1/2 teaspoon ground cumin     1/4 teaspoon paprika (sweet/hot/smoked)     pinch cayenne pepper     1/4 teaspoon salt     1/3 cup extra-virgin olive oil     2 tablespoons minced cilantro or parsley     salt & pepper to taste      Moroccan Dipping Sauce Directions: 1. Whisk lemon juice, garlic, cumin, paprika, cayenne, and salt & pepper. 2. Gradually whisk in the oil; stir in fresh herbs. 3. Serve
